snippet.title: Geopoly Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Welcome to Geopoly!  An NFT based geolocation economic simulator that allows users to rent, buy, upgrade and sell real-life businesses all around the world.

Join the largest capitalist Metaverse in the world 

Ready to build your Real Estate Empire??

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Connect with Geopoly on Social Media

https://www.geopoly.io/
https://t.me/Geopoly_Game
https://twitter.com/Geopoly_Game
https://www.instagram.com/geopoly_game/
